  "texts": [
    "Then we expanded it using GPT-4 to capture synonyms and phrase variants.",
    "We measured preservation as the proportion of experiential terms in the source that appeared in the summary.",
    "To assess sentence coherence, we averaged pairwise cosine similarity between consecutive summary sentences.",
    "A representative excerpt of our experiential lexicon with respective domains is shown in Table 1, with the complete list provided in Appendix A.",
    "Furthermore, the hyperparameter search space of every model is summarized in Table 2."
